effects.display_string: Set: Rage you spend during Rage of the Sleeper fuel the growth of Dream Thorns, which wreath you in their protection after Rage of the Sleeper expires, absorbing 25% of damage dealt to you while the thorns remain, up to 92,301 per 20 Rage spent.

(4) Set: Each 40 Rage you spend while Rage of the Sleeper is active extends its duration by 1.0 sec, up to 5.0. Your Dream Thorns become Blazing Thorns, causing 100% of damage absorbed to be reflected at the attacker.

spells.description:
Equip: The thorns feed off your vitality, reducing Stamina by 129. Your spells and abilities have a chance to launch magical thorns at your target, healing allies for 25,909 or striking enemies for 15,545 Nature damage.

These effects are increased by 100% if you equip an item crafted with a Toxified Armor Patch.
Equip: Increases duration of Well Fed bonuses from Dragon Isles meals by 100% and they now persist through death.
Equip: Taking damage has a chance to call Xeri'tac's brood to your aid, attacking your foes and covering you in protective webbing which absorbs 191,766 damage.
